line_1: To give me credit for a shilling:
For me I wou'd not give a shilling
line_2: GOOD madam, when ladies are willing,

line_1: Tho' it shou'd cost me half a Shilling:
line_2: I'd send it with an Heart most willing,

line_1: To lend him on his Soul a Shilling,
line_2: Who, if some Block-head should be willing
